%p.intro
  Hello #{@user.name},

%p.content
  We're contacting you to let you know that your account at #{link_to Translation.translate('Open Path HMIS Warehouse'), root_url} has been signed into with #{@provider_name} for the first time.

%p.content
  You should now use #{@provider_name} to sign in.

%p.content
  If you not did expect this, please contact your administrator.

%p.closing
  Thank you.
